getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取产品
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select t.product,t1.`name` as productname from zt_projectproduct t left join zt_product t1 on t1.id = t.product where t.project = ? LIMIT 0,1

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取版本
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select t.id as build,case when (select t1.`name` from zt_release t1 where t1.build = t.id and t1.deleted = '0' ORDER BY t1.date desc LIMIT 0,1) is null then t.`name` else (select t1.`name` from zt_release t1 where t1.build = t.id and t1.deleted = '0' ORDER BY t1.date desc LIMIT 0,1) end as buildname from zt_build t where t.project = ? and t.product = ? and t.id =? and t.deleted = '0' LIMIT 0,1
